&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;h3 id=&quot;practice-explore-task&quot;&gt;Practice Explore Task&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are going to finish our internet unit by doing a practice Explore Task. I will be giving you four hours (instead of 8) and limiting your innovations to those relating to the internet.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For today, we‚Äôre going to try out &lt;em&gt;one&lt;/em&gt; of the effective artifact suggestions: the &lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://magic.piktochart.com/templates&quot;&gt;infographic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

