  &lt;li&gt;The domain name system (DNS) translates domain names to IP addresses.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Hierarchy in the DNS helps that system scale.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;The domain name system (DNS) was not designed to be completely secure.&lt;/li&gt;
